## FTC Engineering Process

### Hacker vs Engineer

- Hacker
  - Comes up with solutions on the fly
  - Hard to communicate the solutions
  - Hard to repeat the functions
- Engineer
  - Designs the solution and shares with others


### The Process

- Understand the Problem
- Define the requirements / Capabilities
- Develope a Concept
- Design and Build
- Test

### Tracking Progress

- Using Kanban
- Scrum Meetings
- 